  80,22,"Sinna, ma ihwa yaS, a t id Isker"
  80,23,Xaîi! Ur iuqim ayen i s Iêeppem
  80,24,"Ad iwali tagwella s, umdan"
  80,25,"D Nekwni id Ifkan aman, d ihedman"
  80,26,"Sinna, Ne$za tamurt, d i$isan"
  80,27,"Nessuffe$ ed, segs, iâaqqayen"
