  80,36,"i tmeddakwelt is, akked warraw is"
  80,37,"yal amdan segsen, assen, a d ilhu deg wayen i t iaânan"
  80,38,Ad feooeoen udmawen assen
  80,39,"ad dessen, feôêen"
  80,40,"Assen, udmawen a$webbaô fellasen"
  80,41,Le$wmam idel iten
  80,42,"Widak d ijehliyen, d ucmiten"
  81,1,Ma iu$al itij d akennur
